high_descs: Turn left to the counter top to the left of the sink where the bread loaf is
Pick up the loaf of bread on top of the counter
Carry the bread to the black fridge
Place the bread in the fridge then shut the door and remove the bread, shut the fridge
Carry the bread to the white kitchen table top
Place the bread behind the head of lettuce on top of the table
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled loaf of bread on the table

high_descs: Turn around, take a step then turn right and go to the counter
Pick up the loaf of bread from the front of the counter
Turn right, go to the wall then turn left
Put the bread on the middle shelf in the fridge and wait a bit, then take the bread out of the fridge
Turn around and go to the table
Put the bread on the table
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled loaf of bread on the table

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the counter above the dishwasher.
Pick up the bread on the counter.
Turn to your right and walk to the fridge.
Place the bread in the fridge, wait, and remove it.
Turn around and walk to the white table.
Place the bread on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled loaf of bread on the white table.
